    ActivityComponent
    A component that stores relevant information about activities.

    Enum that denotes which type of activity is performed.

    Manages music and sound effects that are to be played in the game.

    A component that stores relevant information about collisions.

    An abstract class that stores component maps to efficiently receive an entities components.

    Launches the program for desktop PCs.

    Extends the Game class.
    GameObjectComponent
    A component that relevant information about game objects.
    GameObjectComponent.ObjectType
    An enum that holds a value for the type of game object.
    GameOverScreen
    Screen that displays once 7 days have passed and the game has completed.
    GameScreen
    Represents the base class for any game screen implementation.
    GameSystem
    System that handles all logic required with the function of the game, such as the current day or time.
    InputComponent
    A component that stores relevant information about input.
    InputKeys
    Each key that needs to be detected as an input is encoded as a static one-hot value.
    InputSystem
    System that checks for game-relevant keys input by the user.
    MainMenu
    Initial main menu screen that can be used to exit the game or start a new game.
    Map
    Class that is used for storing information about a map that can be displayed by a screen.
    PlayerCameraSystem
    A system that handles updates to a maps camera based on player position.
    PlayerComponent
    A component that stores relevant information about a player.
    PlayerMovementSystem
    System that handles moving a player around a map.
    PlayerSystem
    System that handles what should occur to players given certain actions in the game, for instance if a key is pressed to move a player, the velocity of the player should be modified accordingly.
    PlayScreen
    PlayScreen is the screen that will be displayed during gameplay.
    PositionComponent
    Stores relevant information about position.
    StatBarComponent
    Stores relevant information about statistic bars.
